snippet.title: Persona 3 Reload - (FeMC Mod) 1.9.0 Anniversary Update
snippet.description:
Please read the description.
Happy 1 year anniversary of this mod's release.  It is a small anniversary update but enjoy the changes.  A special Message from Mudkip is in the video please give it a read.

See full patch notes
https://github.com/MadMax1960/Femc-Reloaded-Project/releases/tag/1.9.0

Time Stamp:
0:00 Title Screen has been updated to include FeMC
0:24 A Message from Mudkip the Project Lead
4:58 All Shop Images Replaced by Esa
6:52 Level Up Screens been adjusted fixed by Raycopper (Esa, Ely, Shiosakana artworks)
8:14 Glass Shard Status Screen (ElyAlt) adjusted
8:36 Lisa Bustup has been adjusted
8:57 Gendered Audio Updates by Giowno
11:27 Conclusion Enjoy the Update!!  Bonus Footage

Credits
2D Assets By Esa, Ely, Lisa, Shiosakana, Raycooper
Gendered Audio changes by Giowno
3D Models Mudkip

P3 Reload FEMC mod.  Download the Latest Version from Here.
https://github.com/MadMax1960/Femc-Reloaded-Project/releases
Discord Channel for FeMC Reload Project
https://discord.gg/TyR8RVZeNx

Instructions to Install the Mod:
https://youtu.be/HNYRgqXCzMM?si=_5h-SI9vie43DH7c

Femc Config Adjuster
https://github.com/MadMax1960/Femc-Config-Adjuster/releases
